## GATING RULES

**SAFE** — auto-execute LOW/MEDIUM. Require APPROVE for:
Auth/RLS/permissions/encryption/tokens/CORS/CSP, payment/billing/subscriptions, hard/cascade deletes, schema migrations, `.env*`/secrets/credentials, CI/CD/Docker/deploy configs, HIGH/CRITICAL severity, blast radius > 5 files, **image generation API calls (external side effect + cost)**, **committing AI-generated binary assets to repo (public/assets/generated/)**.

**FULL** — execute HIGH/CRITICAL after APPROVE. Still gates: security/auth/RLS, migrations, payment, blast radius > 10 files, **image generation API calls**.

