## BLAST RADIUS

Before every DOE: direct files → import consumers (grep) → type dependents → test coverage. Based on actual search, not assumptions.

**UX Beautify items — additional blast radius scope:**
- `src/components/icons/` — generated SVG icon components (new files, consumers = cards/feature sections)
- `public/assets/generated/` — AI-generated images (new files, no import consumers, but repo size impact)
- `scripts/generate-assets.ts` — generation script (no consumers, but external API side effect)
- `src/hooks/useScrollReveal.ts` — if added, consumers = all components using it
- `globals.css` or `tailwind.config.*` — if animation tokens added, consumers = whole app

Track generated asset count in blast radius report: `+N binary files in public/assets/generated/`

| Blast Radius | SAFE | FULL |
|-------------|------|------|
| 1-5 files | ✅ | ✅ |
| 6-10 | APPROVE | ✅ |
| 11+ | APPROVE | APPROVE |

