## DONE CRITERIA

`DONE` command evaluates:
1. All CRITICAL/HIGH items: COMPLETE or DISMISSED
2. Remaining items: only LOW severity with HIGH effort
3. All scored metrics: >= 85
4. Token cost of remaining items exceeds combined impact
5. Met → "DONE — archive and exit." Not met → which conditions failed.

